	<h1 class="title">「戛纳电影节」到底有多少东西会出现在大荧幕上？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Niclolas Rapold</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-15 08:27:01 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9583/medium/9583.jpeg?1436675594" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="9583" data-title="《「戛纳电影节」到底有多少东西会出现在大荧幕上？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/9583/medium/9583.jpeg?1436675594" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/9583" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
